  tips:
  - Place bikes strategically - customers browse nearby stations first!
  - Higher rarity bikes = bigger profits, but they take longer to sell
  - Check the weekly race schedule - don't miss out on exclusive discounts!
  - Balance your inventory - stock bikes across all price ranges
  - Upgrade rooms in segments - buy only what you need right now
  - More staff = faster service = happier customers = more sales!
  - Each room upgrade unlocks in pieces - prioritize what helps most
  - Win races to unlock 50% off brand deals - huge savings!
  - VIP customers spend more - make sure your gallery looks impressive
  - Bikes with high Speed sell faster in races, but Handling matters in Circuit tracks
  - Marketing campaigns stack with room bonuses for maximum effect
  - Brand partnerships give exclusive bikes - build reputation to unlock more
  - 'Test Drive Center boosts purchase chances - upgrade it early! '
  - Legendary bikes are rare but worth the investment for collectors
  - Entrance upgrades affect ALL customers - invest here for big returns
  - Higher Acceleration bikes dominate Drag races - choose wisely!
  - 'Upgrade room aesthetics to attract wealthier customers '
  - 'Staff patience matters - upgrade entrance to keep customers happy longer '
  - 'Launch multiple marketing campaigns simultaneously for explosive growth '
  - 'Customers wait in line - upgrade entrance to increase their patience '
  - 'Each race type favors different bike stats - read the descriptions! '
  - 'Complete room levels to unlock new content and decorations '
  - 'Brand reputation unlocks better partnership deals over time '
  - 'Staff can only help one customer at a time - hire more for busy days '
  - 'Weekly races reset every 7 days - plan your schedule! '
  - 'Segment upgrades let you customize your room growth path '
  - 'Marketing Room campaigns are temporary - use them strategically! '
  - 'Test drives increase purchase chance but need good bikes available '
  - 'Room upgrades carry over - you never lose your progress! '
  - '"Every bike has a buyer - you just need to find them!" - Pro Dealer '
  - 'The smell of new tires in the morning... that''s the smell of profit! '
  - 'Some say the perfect gallery has both style AND selection '
  - 'A gallery without customers is just an expensive parking lot '
  - 'Behind every great bike sale is a well-organized showroom '
  - Speed sells bikes, but reputation sells brands
  - 'Your first million starts with your first sale. Get rolling! '
  - 'Customers don''t buy bikes - they buy dreams. Display accordingly! '
  - 'The best upgrade is the one that makes you money back fastest '
  - 'Race hard, sell harder. That''s the dealer way. '
  tipsTitle: Tip
  tipDisplayLength: 1
